HEADWORD: Incorporator
<hw>In*cor"po*ra`tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One of a
number of persons who gets a company incorporated; one of the original
members of a corporation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Incorporeal</ent>⟦br⟧
